## Quick Start

### 1. Local Development
```bash
make setup  # Install dependencies (uv) & pre-commit
make dev    # Start dev server (Hot reload)
```
Visit http://localhost:8000/docs for Swagger UI.

### 2. Docker (Production)
```bash
make up     # Start containers (Builds if needed)
make down   # Stop containers
```

### 3. Testing & Evaluation
```bash
make test   # Run Unit Tests & AI Evals
make lint   # Run Ruff Linter
```

